impact in healthcare. Whether you are seeking short-term contract engagements
or long-term career prospects, AHP Medical provides tailored opportunities to
suit your preferences, both on-site and remotely.

** You will be; **

  * Precisely code medical records employing ICD-10-AM/ACHI/ACS classifications. 
  * Collaborate closely with healthcare professionals to ensure precise documentation. 
  * Methodically review patient charts and reports to allocate accurate codes. 
  * Remain updated on evolving industry coding guidelines and regulations. 
  * Uphold the utmost confidentiality and security of patient information. 

** About You: **

